commit_message:
Register JSON-Home data for resources with inherits

This patch adds support to register json-home data for resources
with inherits.
Some resources gets resigtered along with inherits resource
Currently 'os-volumes_boot' is inhetired from 'servers'
which is used to create server So storing json-home data only for
POST method.

json-home data for resources with inherits will looks like-
{
    "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/rel/servers/os-volumes_boot": {
      "href-template": "/v2.1/{project_id}/servers/{server_id}/os-volumes_boot",
      "href-vars": {
        "project_id": "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/param/project_id",
        "server_id": "http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-compute/2.1/param/server_id"
      }
    }
}

Partially implements blueprint nova-api-json-home

